query: query TvSeriesSoundtracks($tvSeriesId: Long!, $soundtrackLimit: Int = 10) { tvSeries(id: $tvSeriesId) { id soundtrack(limit: $soundtrackLimit) { items { __typename ... on YaMusicSoundtrackAlbum { id __typename } ... on YaMusicSoundtrackPlaylist { id username __typename } } total __typename } __typename } }
